<li id="cite_note-Richardson2004-17"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Richardson2004_17-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Richardson2004_17-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">David Richardson, "Background to annexation: Anglo-African credit relations in the Bight of Biafra, 1700–1891"; in Pétré-Grenouilleau, <i>From Slave Trade to Empire</i> (2004), pp. 47–68.</span>
