<li id="cite_note-40"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-40">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Asiegbu, <i>Nigeria and its British Invaders</i> (1984), pp. xiv, xxviii–xxx.</span>
