<li id="cite_note-57"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-57">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Carland, <i>The Colonial Office and Nigeria</i> (1985), pp. 35–37.</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-Carland1985Egerton-58"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Carland1985Egerton_58-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Carland1985Egerton_58-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">Carland, <i>The Colonial Office and Nigeria</i> (1985), pp. 104–109.</span>
